10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
11 SECTION 3. There is hereby appropriated to the Weigh Station
12 Improvement Revolving Fund, created pursuant to Section 1167 of
13 Title 47 of the Oklahoma Statutes, from any monies not otherwise
14 appropriated from the General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for
15 the fiscal year ending June 30, 2023, the sum of Nine Million
16 Dollars ($9,000,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary to
17 perform the duties imposed upon the Department of Transportation by
18 law.
19 SECTION 4. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
20 SECTION 5. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
21 of the public peace, health and safety, an emergency is hereby
22 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
23 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
